Key Left A $[MOD_KEY] AnimatedMove Screen $[pointer.screen] 0 keep Warp
Key Up A $[MOD_KEY] AnimatedMove Screen $[pointer.screen] keep 0 Warp
Key Down A $[MOD_KEY] AnimatedMove Screen $[pointer.screen] keep -0 Warp
