DestroyFunc Focus-Next-Window
AddToFunc Focus-Next-Window
+ I Next (!WindowListSkip, AcceptsFocus, !Iconic, CurrentPage) Warp-Focus

DestroyFunc Warp-Focus
AddToFunc Warp-Focus
