+ I AddToMenu DynamicWindowOpsMenu "%151-hammer.svg:$[MINI_ICON_SIZE]%Kill" Destroy
+ I AddToMenu DynamicWindowOpsMenu "" Nop
+ I AddToMenu DynamicWindowOpsMenu "%048-folder.svg:$[MINI_ICON_SIZE]%Group Actions" Popup DynamicGroupMenuThingy

